cross: Rhyncattleanthe Elain Taylor x Cattleya Circle of Life

measurements.description: Two round flat flowers on one 6.0-cm inflorescence; sepals orange-red, lateral sepals yellow-orange centrally, magenta veins; petals slightly reflexed at tip, orange-red, magenta veins; lip ruffled, bright gold centrally, scarlet distally and along edge; column and anther cap white; substance firm; texture velvet.
